            <thetext>When you navigate _first time_ to a comboBox with keyboard&#39;s &#39;Tab&#39; key the comboBox will get a blue border indicating that it has the focus. But when you press the &#39;Tab&#39; again the focus remains on the comboBox.

If you debug the process you can see that the next object will get the focus _twice_ but will lose it somehow.
If the next object is a comboBox then the focus will go to the next comboBox.

I&#39;ve made a little example to show this issue.
There is a description to reproduce the bug too:
http://tinyurl.com/34u9zgr</thetext>
